"progressType":0,"referenceIndex":70,"delay":7.800000190734863,"isWaitForSkipMode":0},{"actionType":4,"progressType":0,"referenceIndex":71,"delay":10.649999618530273,"isWaitForSkipMode":0},{"actionType":1,"progressType":1,"referenceIndex":52,"delay":0,"isWaitForSkipMode":0},{"actionType":4,"progressType":0,"referenceIndex":72,"delay":1.649999976158142,"isWaitForSkipMode":0}],"talkData":[{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"... Sigh...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev43-ep2-001","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"So... I have to change...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev43-ep2-002","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"(I've been trying to do everything in my power to help Roselia... to help the others, but I guess maybe that was a bad thing?)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev43-ep2-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"(Yukina has always been easily misunderstood. I thought if I helped keep that from happening too often, everything with the band would go smoothly...)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev43-ep2-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"(... But yeah, it's possible that I've been jumping the gun a little too much. I've always tried very carefully to keep everyone from butting heads. Does this mean I shouldn't have been doing that?)","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":2,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev43-ep2-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"I thought I was doing that to help Yukina, to help the others, but maybe...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev43-ep2-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"... I just wanted people to depend on me...?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev43-ep2-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"In that case, if there's anything that needs to be fixed here, it would be me!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev43-ep2-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"I don't really know if that's the problem or not yet, but it'll probably be better to keep from helping Yukina all the time so that I can know for sure...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev43-ep2-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"... 'Kay. I'll stop giving her so much of my attention! But it doesn't feel right to just stop doing it all at once. Maybe little by little, I should-","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"angry01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev43-ep2-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"... Wah! Yukina?!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev43-ep2-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"...! Lisa? Wh-why do you sound so surprised?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"ev43-ep2-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"You just popped up from around the corner! Of course I'd be surprised~! And I was in the middle of thinking about something, so yeah...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev43-ep2-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"Thinking about what?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"ev43-ep2-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Huh? Oh no, it's~... Hahaha...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev43-ep2-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"Yukina","body":"...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"ev43-ep2-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"Ahaha~... Sigh...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev43-ep2-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"windowDisplayName":"Lisa","body":"W-we ended up walking home together, but... th-this is pretty awkward~...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":23,"motionName":"uwame01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":23,"voiceId":"ev43-ep2-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":23}],"window